data.description: Beautiful Buckeye Horse Property, large split floor-plan with neutral colors. Kitchen has plenty of cabinets, island, double oven, new dishwasher. Living room and family room. The bedrooms are large with walk in closets. New sliding glass door, vinyl flooring. The back yard has a full length patio (not attached). 5 shaded horse stalls with water nearby. Beautiful landscaping. 2 large sheds. Plenty of space on this flat lot.
